  "title": "Sales and Marketing",
  "description": "<p><br />We're looking for self-assured, friendly, and motivated people to join our team! If you like interacting with people, forming relationships, and making money through your efforts, this position is for you. As a Sales Specialist, you will be the amiable face of our business, interacting with clients, offering innovative solutions, and developing alongside a lively and encouraging team.</p><p>There are no dull days here only development, education, and positive energy!</p><p>Join us, where your contributions are valued, your progress is unrestricted, and your voice matters.</p><p>Start your journey with us by applying right now!<br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Key responsibilities:</p><p>* Be the Voice of Our Brand: Make outgoing calls to prospective clients and explain what makes our goods and services intriguing and worthwhile.</p><p>* Establish True Connections: Learn about others, comprehend their needs, and suggest solutions that genuinely benefit them.</p><p>* Be the Voice of Our Brand: Make outgoing calls to prospective clients and explain what makes our goods and services intriguing and worthwhile.</p><p>* Establish True Connections: Learn about others, comprehend their needs, and suggest solutions that genuinely benefit them.</p><p>*Create Great Customer Experiences: Respond to inquiries and issues in a professional manner while providing upbeat, amiable service.</p><p>* Work as a Team: Cooperate and share ideas on how to achieve team and individual goals and progress together. <br /><br /><br />Advantages:</p><p>* Ongoing instruction and skill improvement</p><p>* A vibrant, inclusive, and encouraging team environment</p><p>* Unambiguous career advancement and international prospects</p><p>* Incentives and rewards depending on performance<br /></p><p>What We Are Seeking:</p><p>* Excellent written and verbal communication abilities<br /><br />* A warm, self-assured, and vivacious disposition</p><p>* While not required, prior telesales or customer care experience is a plus!</p><p>* At ease in a fast-paced, goal-oriented workplace <br /><br />* A readiness to grow, learn, and adapt</p><p>* A self-driven and optimistic outlook<br /></p><p><br /><br /></p><p>R25156061</p><p>Just Recruit Singapore Pte Ltd - EA12C6295</p>",
